#								-*-conf-*-
OASISFormat: 0.3
Name:        omd
Version:     0.1
Synopsis:    A Markdown frontend in pure OCaml.
Description: This Markdown library has no dependency besides the OCaml
  compiler.  The implementation targets the original Markdown with a few
  Github markdown features.
Authors:     Philippe Wang <philippe.wang@gmail.com>
Maintainers: Philippe Wang <philippe.wang@gmail.com>
License:     ISC
Homepage:    https://github.com/pw374/omd
Plugins:     META (0.3), StdFiles (0.3)

Library "omd"
  Path:         src
  BuildTools:   ocamlbuild
  Modules:      Omd_utils, Omd_representation, Omd_backend, Omd_lexer, Omd_parser, Omd

Executable "omd"
  Path:         src
  BuildTools:   ocamlbuild
  MainIs:       omd_main.ml
  BuildDepends: omd
  CompiledObject: best

